Polish consumer confidence up in April . Polish consumer confidence indicators , measured by the Demoskop polling institute for the Rzeczpospolita daily , increased in April , Demoskop said on Tuesday . Demoskop ' s consumer confidence index was at 101 points in April , up one point from February . It was at 102 points in February . The business climate index rose to 99 points in April from 94 in March and the index measuring propensity to spend fell to 102 points from 104 points . @ The Demoskop survey was carried out between April 9 - 14 among a representative random sample of 994 adult Poles . - - Warsaw Newsroom + 48 22 653 9700 
